<LocalTag Name="muutosnopeus" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Current speed of change (Process value unit per minute)]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="KeskiarvoSumma" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Sum of average value]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="KeskiarvoLaskuri" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Average value counter]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Edellisen_Kierroksen_Prosessin_Keskiarvo" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Previous scan average process value]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Prosessiarvon_Keskiarvo" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Process value average]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Edellisen_Kierroksen_Muutosnopeus" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Change speed of previous scan (Process value unit per minute)]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="TavoiteMuutosnopeus" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Target speed of change (1+ Integral term) / 60]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="TavoiteKuroutumisaika_min" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[(min)]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Kiihtyvyys" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Rate of change (per scan)]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Ennustettu_Muutosnopeus_Tulevaisuuteen" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Predictable speed of change in future (Process value unit per minute)]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Edellisen_Kierroksen_Kiihtyvyys" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Rate of change of previous scan]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="OUTPUTKORJAUS" DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Output value correction %]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0.00000000e+000]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="REAL" Radix="Float" Value="0.0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
</LocalTags>
<Routines>
<Routine Name="Logic" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Set Timer 0..30 seconds

]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[MOVE(30000,Ajastin.PRE)TON(Ajastin,?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Update process average value to filter fluctuation
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[ADD(KeskiarvoSumma,Prosessiarvo,KeskiarvoSumma)ADD(KeskiarvoLaskuri,1,KeskiarvoLaskuri);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Proceed when at least one scan is performed 
and 
30 second time has elapsed or update time is done
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[GE(Ajastin.ACC,Paivitys_Aika_ms) ,XIC(Ajastin.DN) ]GT(KeskiarvoLaskuri,1)MCR();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Count process value momentary speed of change
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[DIV(KeskiarvoSumma,KeskiarvoLaskuri,Prosessiarvon_Keskiarvo)CPT(muutosnopeus,60*(Prosessiarvon_Keskiarvo-Edellisen_Kierroksen_Prosessin_Keskiarvo)/(Ajastin.ACC/1000));]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Count acceleration and filter the value

]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CPT(Kiihtyvyys,muutosnopeus-Edellisen_Kierroksen_Muutosnopeus)CPT(Kiihtyvyys,(Kiihtyvyys+Edellisen_Kierroksen_Kiihtyvyys)/2);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Filter speed of change value: Current  speed - Previous speed value.
Count Error value (Setpoint - Process value average) 

]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CPT(muutosnopeus,(muutosnopeus+Edellisen_Kierroksen_Muutosnopeus)/2)SUB(SetPoint,Prosessiarvon_Keskiarvo,Ero);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Count Target value for speed of change according to the Integral term value
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CPT(TavoiteKuroutumisaika_min,(1+I)/60)DIV(Ero,TavoiteKuroutumisaika_min,TavoiteMuutosnopeus);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Count predictable speed of change in future according to the acceleration value and Derivative term
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CPT(Ennustettu_Muutosnopeus_Tulevaisuuteen,muutosnopeus+Kiihtyvyys*(D*1000/Ajastin.ACC));]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Count output value correction]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CPT(OUTPUTKORJAUS,(Ajastin.ACC/1000)*0.001*P*((TavoiteMuutosnopeus-((muutosnopeus+Ennustettu_Muutosnopeus_Tulevaisuuteen)/2))*(SQRT(ABS(Ero))+1)+Ero));]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Balance output correction value If output correction is too high
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[NE(Max_Delta_Output_Per_s,0)CMP((ABS(OUTPUTKORJAUS))>(Max_Delta_Output_Per_s*Ajastin.ACC/1000))CPT(OUTPUTKORJAUS,(ABS(OUTPUTKORJAUS)/OUTPUTKORJAUS)*Max_Delta_Output_Per_s*Ajastin.ACC/1000);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="10" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Output % value with correction  
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[ADD(OUTPROSENTTI,OUTPUTKORJAUS,OUTPROSENTTI);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="11" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Force output value 100 %
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[GT(OUTPROSENTTI,100)MOVE(100,OUTPROSENTTI);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="12" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Force output value 0 %
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[LT(OUTPROSENTTI,0)MOVE(0,OUTPROSENTTI);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="13" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Update previous scan values and reset 30 second timer
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[MOVE(Kiihtyvyys,Edellisen_Kierroksen_Kiihtyvyys)MOVE(muutosnopeus,Edellisen_Kierroksen_Muutosnopeus)MOVE(Prosessiarvon_Keskiarvo,Edellisen_Kierroksen_Prosessin_Keskiarvo)MOVE(0,KeskiarvoLaskuri)MOVE(0,KeskiarvoSumma)RES(Ajastin);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
</AddOnInstructionDefinition>
<AddOnInstructionDefinition Name="T_ADD" Revision="1.0" RevisionExtension="00 Release" Vendor="Rockwell Automation" ExecutePrescan="false" ExecutePostscan="false" ExecuteEnableInFalse="false" CreatedDate="2008-04-08T21:16:05.802Z" CreatedBy="Not Available" EditedDate="2009-04-23T20:13:43.291Z" EditedBy="Not Available"
 SoftwareRevision="v16.03">
<Description>
<![CDATA[DateTime := DateTime + Time]]>
</Description>
<RevisionNote>
<![CDATA[Initial formal release]]>
</RevisionNote>
<AdditionalHelpText>
<![CDATA[T_Add : Add Date/Time plus Time to get new Date/Time

This instruction adds a given amount of Time to a Date/Time to arrive at a new Date/Time.  The new Date/Time is "normalized", that is, given as a valid (if possible) Gregorian Date and Time:

*  0 <= Microseconds < 1,000,000
*  0 <= Seconds < 60    (NOTE: this instruction cannot add leap seconds;  sorry!)
*  0 <= Minutes < 60
*  0 <= Hours < 24
*  1 <= Day <= 31 AND Date is a Valid Gregorian Date (see below)
*  1 <= Month <= 12

NOTE:  This instruction does NOT switch to Julian dates for dates before 1582 (or 1753 or whenever your place of interest switched to the Gregorian Calendar -- see Wikipedia on "Gregorian Calendar" for details)!  This instruction assumes the Gregorian Calendar extends "indefinitely" (about 5.8 million years) either side of "zero" CE!  It DOES handle the Gregorian 4 / 100 / 400 year rules, so Feb. 29, 2000 is a valid date, but Feb. 29, 2100 is not.  It DOES NOT handle Daylight Savings Time hour offsets when the amount of Time added carries the Date/Time across summer/winter time boundaries.
]]>
</AdditionalHelpText>
<Parameters>
<Parameter Name="EnableIn" TagType="Base" DataType="BOOL" Usage="Input" Radix="Decimal" Required="false" Visible="false" ExternalAccess="Read Only">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Enable Input - System Defined Parameter]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="EnableOut" TagType="Base" DataType="BOOL" Usage="Output" Radix="Decimal" Required="false" Visible="false" ExternalAccess="Read Only">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Enable Output - System Defined Parameter]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="Ref_DT" TagType="Base" DataType="DateTime" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false">
<Description>
<![CDATA[DT (Date/Time) to which to add Time]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="Ref_Time" TagType="Base" DataType="DateTime" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Time to be added to DT (Date/Time)]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="Ref_Out" TagType="Base" DataType="DateTime" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Date/Time = DT+Time]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
</Parameters>
<LocalTags>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_YrFromMo" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Number of Years to add from Months]]>
</Description>
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_DaFromHr" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
