<![CDATA[Alarm 32-64
status]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].0">
<![CDATA[32. Alarm: DEC filter temperature channel fault]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].1">
<![CDATA[33. Alarm:
Water tank temperature channel fault]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].2">
<![CDATA[34. Alarm: Circulation water tank level low]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].3">
<![CDATA[35 Alarm: Emergency stop pressed]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].4">
<![CDATA[36. Alarm: Product temp probe failure]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].5">
<![CDATA[37. Alarm: Pneumatic Interlock failure]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].6">
<![CDATA[Alarm 38: Plant steam pressure low]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].7">
<![CDATA[39. Alarm: Air detected in drain]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].8">
<![CDATA[40. Alarm:
Air detection
temp channel fault]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[1].9">
<![CDATA[41. Alarm: 
Fieldbus Failure]]>
