<Tag Name="Option" TagType="Base" DataType="OPTIONS" Constant="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write" OpcUaAccess="None">
<Comments>
<Comment Operand=".CA_PROCESS">
<![CDATA[Option CA-process
(C-option must be unselected)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".C_PROCESS">
<![CDATA[Option 01.1.2.2
C-process, select this with SAMX also
(CA-option must be
unselected)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DEC_PROCESS">
<![CDATA[Option 01.1.3.2
Decontamination
Cycle]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DEC_TV1153">
<![CDATA[Option 01.1.3.2 DEC & chamber size > 4 m3]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DECV_PROCESS">
<![CDATA[Option 01.1.3.3 Decontamination Virasure Cycle]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".SAMX_PROCESS">
<![CDATA[Option 01.1.9.2 SAMX process (C-option have to be selected also with SAMX)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".VHP_PROCESS">
<![CDATA[Option VHP
Isolator Interface (ex 10.4.19)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".VHP_BIODEC">
<![CDATA[Option 10.4.41 VHP_Ready STERIS VHP 1000ED]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".VHP_PORTS">
<![CDATA[Option  VHP_Ports (ex 10.4.40)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".HPPD">
<![CDATA[Option 10.2.3
Heated Pressurized Pulse Drying]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".FILTER_STER">
<![CDATA[Option 10.2.4
Air Filter
Sterilization]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".FILT_CONDENSATE_TV2163">
<![CDATA[Option 10.2.4 AND: Chamber height > 12 or Chamber height = 9 and Option 10.4.73.1 filter housing 10" RST]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".ATM_AIR_LINE">
<![CDATA[ATM air line in HMI Piping screen: Select when chamber volume > 1380 L (size class >= 2)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DIN_PRECYCLE">
<![CDATA[DIN Leak Rate Test included]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".TANK_LS896">
<![CDATA[Option 10.2.7 Cooling water saving
tank for pump]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".VAC_PUMP_WATER_SAVE">
<![CDATA[Option 10.2.8  Domestic Cooling Water Recycling Package for Vacuum Pump and Effluent Cooling]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".PRESS_UNIT">
<![CDATA[0 = kPa
1 = Psia]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LOAD_1">
<![CDATA[Load 1 temperature, always selected = standard (ex option 10.3.1)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LOAD_2">
<![CDATA[Option 10.3.3
Load 2 temperature]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LOAD_3">
<![CDATA[Option 10.3.3
Load 3 temperature]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LOAD_4">
<![CDATA[Option 10.3.3
Load 4 temperature]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".ST_PANEL">
<![CDATA[Option 10.3.2.1 ST-side Operator panel]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".ST_INDICATOR_LIGHTS">
<![CDATA[ST indicator
lights valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".RECORDER">
<![CDATA[Option 10.3.4 or Option 10.3.8 Recorder valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".GROUND_FAULT_IND">
<![CDATA[GFI ( ex option 10.3.11)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".UPS_BATTERY">
<![CDATA[Option 10.3.12 
Uninterruptible
Power Supply]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DOUBLE_DOOR">
<![CDATA[0 = 1 door 1 = 2 door]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".COND_LEVEL_LS895">
<![CDATA[Condensate
level switch
Not Option 10.4.7]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".PLANT_STEAM">
<![CDATA[Option 10.4.60 Jacket heated
with plant steam]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".JACKET_CLOSED_LOOP">
<![CDATA[Option10.2.9 Closed loop cascade jacket cooling  (select also option10.2.7, not 10.2.8)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".EJECTOR">
<![CDATA[Option Ejector selected, used with CX, do not select with norm. SAMX option]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".AIR_DETECTOR">
<![CDATA[Option 10.4.63 HTM2010
Air detection
selected]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".STEAM_PS800">
<![CDATA[PS800 Steam utility pressure
switch valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".STEAM_PS801">
<![CDATA[PS801 Plant steam
utility switch]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".COMP_AIR_PS802">
<![CDATA[PS802 Comp air pressure
switch valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".COMP_AIR_PV211">
<![CDATA[PV211
Compressed air to chamber]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".WATER_PS804">
<![CDATA[PS804 Water pressure
switch valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".C_WATER_PS823">
<![CDATA[PS823 Cooling water
perssure switch valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".BLEEDER_YY612">
<![CDATA[Trad GMP
Chamber top bleeder]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".COND_EXHAUST_YY632">
<![CDATA[Trad GMP
Condensate Exhaust (Select with SAMX process)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".RUPTURE_PZV827">
<![CDATA[PZV827 Rupture disc & alarm valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".SAFETY_RELIEF_VALVE_PZV827">
<![CDATA[PZV827 Safety relief valve with switch & alarm valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".SCADA_HANDSHAKE">
<![CDATA[Handshake + alarm
valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".STATUS_RELAYS">
<![CDATA[K400, K500
and K600
relays valid]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".SELF_CLEANING_STRAINER">
<![CDATA[LSR Option
Self Cleaning Strainer]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LSR_STERILIZER">
<![CDATA[0 = BPS  1 = LSR type sterilizer = 138 C max exp. temp.]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DATE">
<![CDATA[0 = mm/dd/year
1 = dd.mm.year]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".DOOR_TYPE">
<![CDATA[0 = Horizontal
1 = Vertical (pysty)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".PI_DIAGRAM">
<![CDATA[1 = Process Diagram screen enabled]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".EN285_MONITORING">
<![CDATA[EN285 Independent Monitoring (10.4.65).
Also uncheck Inhibit from GX10 module.]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".TEST_DI">
<![CDATA[Simulate Digital Inputs
for test only]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".TEST_AI">
<![CDATA[Simulate
Analog Inputs
for test only]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".TEST_FESTO_DIAGNOSTICS">
<![CDATA[Simulate
Festo diagnostics
for test only]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".PRINTER_TYPE">
<![CDATA[0 = CUSTOM PLUS2 / ALFAP
1 = CUSTOM PLUS4 / EPSON 
2 = LASERJET]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".USB_BATCH_DATA">
<![CDATA[Not in use, reserved for future option: 1 = Batch data to TXT file]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LANGUAGE">
<![CDATA[0 = only Eng,
other = bit selections]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LANGUAGE.1">
<![CDATA[English enabled]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LANGUAGE.2">
<![CDATA[Finnish enabled]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LANGUAGE.3">
<![CDATA[Swedish enabled]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LANGUAGE.4">
<![CDATA[Spanish enabled]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".LANGUAGE.5">
<![CDATA[France enabled]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".FESTO_AI_MODULES">
<![CDATA[Number of AI modules at FESTO terminal
(mA + RTDs)
2-4]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".FESTO_DO_MODULES">
<![CDATA[Number of Valve Modules at Festo terminal (3 or 4)]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".FESTO_DI_MODULES">
<![CDATA[Number of Festo DI modules  1 -3]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".FESTO_AO_MODULES">
<![CDATA[Number of AO modules at FESTO terminal
0 - 2 (select 1 with SAMX)]]>
</Comment>
</Comments>
