for pressure]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".PRECOND_1_TYPE">
<![CDATA[0 = None
1 = Forced
2 = Pulsed
3 = DEC
4 = SAMX Heating Up]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand=".PRECOND_2_TYPE">
<![CDATA[0 = None
1 = Forced
2 = Pulsed]]>
