<Routine Name="DO_move" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Move digital outputs
to the output card]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Digital output status for the Operator Interface

Festo digital output addresses depending on number of Analog output modules (0 - 2) located before valve blocks:
No analog output module: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 2 -5
One analog output module: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 6 - 9
Two analog output modules: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 10 - 13]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[COP(Local:2:O,DIG_OUT_View[0],1) ,LT(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) MOVE(4,Valve_DO_start_addr2) ,[EQ(Option.Festo_AO_modules,0) [MOVE(2,Valve_DO_start_addr) ,EQ(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) MOVE(5,Valve_DO_start_addr2) ] ,EQ(Option.Festo_AO_modules,1) [MOVE(6,Valve_DO_start_addr) ,EQ(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) MOVE(9,Valve_DO_start_addr2) ] ,EQ(Option.Festo_AO_modules,2) [MOVE(10,Valve_DO_start_addr) ,EQ(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) MOVE(13,Valve_DO_start_addr2) ] ] ,BTD(U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr],0,DIG_OUT_View[1],0,8) [BTD(U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr+1],0,DIG_OUT_View[1],8,8) BTD(U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr+2],0,DIG_OUT_View[1],16,8) ,EQ(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) BTD(U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr2],0,DIG_OUT_View[1],24,8) ,BTD(U784:O.Data[10],0,DIG_OUT_View[2],0,8) ,BTD(U784:O.Data[11],0,DIG_OUT_View[2],8,8) ] ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Move digital outputs to the output card
Normal mode

Festo digital output addresses depending on number of Analog output modules (0 - 2) located before valve blocks:
No analog output module: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 2 -5
One analog output module: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 6 - 9
Two analog output modules: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 10 - 13]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(Process.Running) ,XIO(HMI.DO_force) ,LE(Password_level,3) ][COP(DIG_OUT[0],Local:2:O,16) ,BTD(DIG_OUT[1],0,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr],0,8) BTD(DIG_OUT[1],8,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr+1],0,8) [BTD(DIG_OUT[1],16,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr+2],0,8) ,EQ(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) BTD(DIG_OUT[1],24,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr2],0,8) ,BTD(DIG_OUT[2],0,U784:O.Data[10],0,8) ,BTD(DIG_OUT[2],8,U784:O.Data[11],0,8) ] ,COP(DIG_OUT[0],DIG_OUT_Force[0],3) ,OTU(HMI.DO_force) RET() ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Move forced  digital outputs to the output card when service mode

Festo digital output addresses depending on number of Analog output modules (0 - 2) located before valve blocks:
No analog output module: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 2 -5
One analog output module: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 6 - 9
Two analog output modules: adresses FESTO_FB32:O.Data 10 - 13]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(HMI.DO_force)[COP(DIG_OUT_Force[0],Local:2:O,16) ,BTD(DIG_OUT_Force[1],0,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr],0,8) BTD(DIG_OUT_Force[1],8,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr+1],0,8) [BTD(DIG_OUT_Force[1],16,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr+2],0,8) ,EQ(Option.Festo_DO_modules,4) BTD(DIG_OUT_Force[1],24,U784:O.Data[Valve_DO_start_addr2],0,8) ,BTD(DIG_OUT_Force[2],0,U784:O.Data[10],0,8) ,BTD(DIG_OUT_Force[2],8,U784:O.Data[11],0,8) ] ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="Festo_Ethernet" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Festo Module status information is transferred to Festo_Status[0] tag
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(Option.Test_Festo_diagnostics)GSV(Module,U784,EntryStatus,Festo_Status[0]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Following 4 rungs change and move diagnostic information to Festo_Status[1] tag 
0 = Standby - Controller is powering up
1 = Faulted 
2 = Validating
3 = Connecting
4 = Runnning = Normal Operation
5 = Shutting Down
6 = Inhibited
7 = Waiting]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CLR(Festo_Status[1]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(Festo_Status[0].12)MOVE(1,Festo_Status[1]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(Festo_Status[0].13)CPT(Festo_Status[1],Festo_Status[1]+2);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(Festo_Status[0].14)CPT(Festo_Status[1],Festo_Status[1]+4);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Create indexing number for festo according to the number of  AI modules]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[CPT(Festo_AI_Index,Option.Festo_AI_modules*8-2);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Create indexing number2 for festo according to the number of  AI modules
tag indexing must be compatible also when there is only 2 AI modules in festo terminal]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[EQ(Option.Festo_AI_modules,2) MOVE(6,Festo_AI_Index_2) ,GT(Option.Festo_AI_modules,2) MOVE(14,Festo_AI_Index_2) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Festo Internal diagnostics information is transferred to Festo_Status[2] tag]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[BTD(U784:I.Data[0],0,Festo_Status[2],0,8);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Make Festo internal diagnostics faulted if connection is lost]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[NE(Festo_Status[1],4)MOVE(255,Festo_Status[2]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
