<![CDATA[YY661 PV161 PV161.1 Pressure Exhaust from 
NS seal]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[YY661 PV161 PV161.1 Pressure exhaust NS seal]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[LIMIT(2,Process.Step,3) ,LIMIT(29,Process.Step,31) ]NE(Process.Service_cycle,2)OTE(DIG_OUT[1].8);]]>
