<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[FIT AND WATER TANK SANITIZATION
Initial upstream gas volume: xx ml
Maximum surrounding temperatures: xx C
Minimum test water temperature: xx C
Maximum test water temperature: xx C
Feed water branch flush time: xx sec]]>
</Comment>
